spokesman told a news conference that it was more important that 
the communist party members realizethat we are living in a 
different age and elect a central committee that would act on that 
reform policy 
he said several of the more than 30 speakers who took the floor 
tuesday criticized zhivkovs rule and the administrative 
bureaucratic system that allowed it others he said supported 
mladenovs call for dialogue with independent groups 
