other project of its type in the country the program is funded by 
a 600000 threeyear grant from the national institute of health 
its not so much how to take care of their illness as how to 
deal with daytoday living how to get a bus schedule how to 
prepare snacks it also guides someone through decisionmaking 
such as where to live or whether to take a new drug ms brennan 
said 
