faulty connector on an electronics box had to be replaced 
once the fueling began the launch pad had to be cleared of all 
nonessential personnel because it is dangerous that prevented 
workers from making up lost time in other areas 
work was running late even before the connector problem because 
of difficulties working with new systems on a mobile launch 
platform being used for the first time and with the launch pad 
