said a sticking point is denards demand for a guarantee he will 
not be prosecuted in france for his role in an unsuccessful 1977 
coup in the west african country of benin 
comorans widely blame denard for abdallahs death according to 
various sources the two men argued about several matters just 
before the shooting 
denard helped engineer a coup that ousted abdallah in 1975 the 
year the island nation became independent from france 
